&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;FormativGroup is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Aladdin Front Office Consultant&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing Financial Services practice. In this role, you&#39;ll work closely with investment and trading teams, leveraging &lt;strong&gt;BlackRock Aladdin Front Office&lt;/strong&gt; capabilities to support daily trading operations, optimize workflows, and reduce operational risk. The ideal candidate brings hands-on Aladdin experience, a strong understanding of investment operations, and the ability to collaborate across front, middle, and back-office teams in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Support and oversee front-office trading activities within the BlackRock Aladdin platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Coordinate and monitor the complete trade lifecycle, ensuring accurate execution from order creation through settlement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Perform cash, position, and transaction validations using Excel and SQL to identify discrepancies and mitigate operational risk.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
