&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Identify emerging operational risks and communicate issues quickly to the appropriate stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
