&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a proven, consultative sales professional who has successfully engaged C-level stakeholders and driven complex Data &amp;amp; Analytics or data platform solutions? Do you thrive in discovery-led environments where you uncover client challenges, shape strategy, and build pipeline around transformation initiatives rather than selling a predefined product?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
