&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&qu

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Data Strategy and Governance Manager will help clients design, implement, and mature enterprise data strategy and data governance programs that support data quality, cloud transformation, analytics, AI readiness, and long-term business value.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;FormativGroup provides technology consulting and engineering services that help mid-sized enterprises modernize operations, streamline data architecture, integrate applications, and enable AI-driven workflows. This role sits within the Data &amp;amp; Analytics practice and will serve as both a trusted client advisor and internal delivery leader.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
