&lt;li&gt;Support project solutioning activities including requirements gathering, estimation, roadmap planning, implementation strategy, and change management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in pre-sales and business development activities including scoping workshops, statement of work reviews, effort estimation, and client presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide leadership and mentorship to delivery teams, including offshore and remote resources, while fostering accountability, collaboration, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate deployment readiness, testing activities, UAT support, release management, and production cutover planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain strong client relationships while positioning FormativGroup as a trusted advisor and strategic delivery partner.&lt;/li&gt;
